description:
The pattern:
    def _addr(value: IPv6Address | str) -> IPv6Address:
        return value if isinstance(value, IPv6Address) else IPv6Address(value)

Appears identically in: router.py, routing.py, dao.py, discovery.py, cache.py, error.py, gradient.py, processor.py.

Fix: Single _addr in a shared module (e.g., lichen.util or lichen.ipv6).
